Returns: If true, the plural variant (which takes a collection and adds each element inside) will treat null as an empty collection, i.e. do nothing. If false (the default), it is null checked as if annotated with @lombok.NonNull.
The singular annotation is used together with @Builder to create single element 'add' methods in the builder for collections.
